{"tid":137047,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"3310 復活 重製 發表！","createTime":"2017-02-27T13:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T09:51:46.000Z","uid":2515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc44561e12eddf957b0d9fe92609111f7f670b3","tid":137047,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/27/215406_6ce701a0df33f69ab61d81410c927460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F27%2F215406_6ce701a0df33f69ab61d81410c927460.jpg&h=7b50597c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNokia  剛剛於MWC 2017 發佈了經典手提電話 3310的重啟版本，將於2017年第2季度開售，售價為49歐，約500港幣。<br />\n <br />\n經典的3310相信各位7、80後都不會陌生，當年超級長氣的電量 (印象中可以用最少1個星期不用叉電) ，憑著優秀的續航力，無堅不摧的機身，加上最強的消閒App - 貪食蛇，曾經風麾一時。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，今次的重製版的續航力也不差，擁有22小時的通話時間、長達1個月的待機電力、16MB的內存(支援最高32GB的microSD card)、2.4吋的QVGA螢幕、2G的上網能力、運行 Nokia Series 30+ OS。當然也保留了「貪食蛇」(當然是新的版本)，有4種顏色選擇，micro-USB 叉電口。<br />\n<br />\n 鏡頭方面的配置就相當抱歉，只配置了一個200萬像的主鏡頭，但當然，3310的粉絲應該毫不介意。<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自photoblog"},{"pid":"1014244e4679e95bb9ab48e3d277cce161da88af","tid":137047,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"我唔知道有無巴打用過<br />\n呢部鬼打野 真係好能襟用<br />\n跌又跌得 電量又勁小<br />\n當年佢同8250真係雙雄"},{"pid":"96f512f5873ccb89324615b2fdb6a868a150d067","tid":137047,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔知道有無巴打用過<br />\n呢部鬼打野 真係好能襟用<br />\n跌又跌得 電量又勁小<br />\n當年佢同8250真係雙雄</blockquote><br />\n8250正好多"},{"pid":"811a34c0c3cb45c10a63134e47b4b90c06f65f10","tid":137047,"uid":19789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"啲料會唔會冇以前咁襟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf4b9c90a928544e726d391831526c1f5ad5caa","tid":137047,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"2g 上網........"},{"pid":"e9e220703ad838829927903956f3bba6660fac6f","tid":137047,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"軍火商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa62c3de7d007fe5a84a352a851fe01b4532b73","tid":137047,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"通話係3G？"},{"pid":"514dd225a97930ee73325c2d310067de8f2ccd94","tid":137047,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"拎黎開工粗用都抵"},{"pid":"7178adb95e1dcdbfc74a5123569e91b67c6e6cad","tid":137047,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎黎開工粗用都抵</blockquote><br />\n開工用minimum都要用到whatsapp"},{"pid":"d523bc85535ba977611790cc6daea18add893b33","tid":137047,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2g 上網........</blockquote><br />\n當時上網唔係最主要用途，當年買3310都係因為價錢平(相比當時既8210、8250)，既可以打電話玩SMS，又可以玩好多個人化設定(例如：入歌仔做鈴聲(midi)、屏幕圖像等、換機殼等)。<br />\n只係因為而家科技發達，上網先變得越來越重要。<br />\n就算後繼機3330，雖然都可以上網，不過唔係用GPRS制式，而係用WAP上網，只係因為當時用手機上網都係以文字為主，所以所需嘅數據好少(不過當時嘅數據價錢好貴，唔係上台都用唔到。)"},{"pid":"7137909b3744ad65c39bed4e387b73f20ac35023","tid":137047,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"其實真係買個回憶定點...？<br />\n<br />\n係呢個年代仲用唔用到"},{"pid":"399c51d59b571ccd8aa211f845029896e360cffe","tid":137047,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實真係買個回憶定點...？<br />\n<br />\n係呢個年代仲用唔用到</blockquote><br />\n香港都就快冇2g頻譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa7e021bd2fa00a5377ab645e7eceaf151502ad","tid":137047,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"買嚟留念都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/g